3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper deals with coordination between agents, which is a key problem in artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) - The paper deals with coordination between multiple agents, which is a core concept in multi-agent systems.
